{"tid":467051,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"狼人 Whatsapp group","createTime":"2017-11-13T06:57:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-22T02:50:22.000Z","uid":87480,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"e6e57aaee4bf3336677a57309ad22731e8d83ee4","tid":467051,"uid":87480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T06:57:28.000Z","msg":"可能有人會講，點解要用whatsapp，telegram 有bot<br />\n首先我地group 內嘅人都玩左三年，都試過玩telegram<br />\n試過好多個group，都發現玩telegram bot 嘅遊戲時間太短，冇討論冇心戰。<br />\n可能係我地咁岩入啲group啲人亂嚟，其他唔會係咁。<br />\n都可能有人講telegram 都可以唔用bot，學返whatsapp MC 狼咁嘅模式。<br />\n不過唔緊要，我地都累喇，成班人都係用開whatsapp，唔想再試telegram喇。<br />\n<br />\n至於娘娘狗公問題<br />\n牛唔飲水唔撳得牛頭低<br />\n我地控制唔到<br />\n有人投訴就踢<br />\n<br />\n我地淨係需要你參與遊戲就得，始於愈大場愈好玩<br />\n<br />\n想了解多啲嘅，telegram 我先<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/Samb8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FSamb8&d=k57gxErVPdcx3EMewoHKX%2F7vEz4FU%2Bq4m%2F6ZFrWLoTs%3D&h=42fe5d14\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Samb8</a>"},{"pid":"5c48e4f75d0f0fb9d10846683e4210830e801478","tid":467051,"uid":87480,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T07:00:32.000Z","msg":"狼狼狼 女預守村村 愛吹野<br />\n職業:<br />\n<br />\n狼：mc會開一個grp 互相知道對方係狼 方便狼人討論戰略<br />\n<br />\n女：救被狼殺害 和 毒一個人<br />\n兩者可同一晚使用（救同毒一次性）<br />\n<br />\n預：每回合晚上選擇其中一人 並向mc 查問其身份（職業）<br />\n<br />\n守：每回合晚上守護一個人 使該人免於被狼人殺害 可以守護自己 但不能連續兩晚守同一個人<br />\n<br />\n村：完全沒有能力 但投狼時 影響勝負<br />\n<br />\n愛：第一晚 詢問mc 選擇兩人為情侶<br />\n情侶互相知道對方是情侶 但情侶不知誰是愛 愛需要盡力你選擇的情侶贏<br />\n<br />\n吹:每rd標記2-3人 標記哂就贏<br />\n<br />\n野: 揀一個人做老母老母死野變狼老母未死 野係好人<br />\n<br />\n學下術語先：<br />\n跳-講你咩職，當然可以講大話<br />\n笠-本來跳左a職，改跳b 職就叫笠職<br />\nV- 投票<br />\n暗票-偷偷投一個人<br />\nPC-警察，投一個人計兩票<br />\nW - 狼<br />\n<br />\n投票格式（pm mc）：<br />\n你個名 v 對方 pc/w<br />\n<br />\n投票方法<br />\nmc 每round cut前 pm mc投票<br />\nCut 後投票一律唔計<br />\n<br />\n提示：<br />\n我地通常玩都會跳職，可以提供多啲線索俾自己人認隊友。狼跳假職可以誤導好人。<br />\n你戰術上當然可以潛，無話一定要上水，但有可能玩死隊友。<br />\n<br />\n唔好係狼game 用輸賭方式說服人，除非你賭j 找jj 數<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBtw 睇睇新人<br />\n玩狼期間，夜晚no game talk(MC 處分)<br />\n日間no 亂入及屍變（違者踢出gp 直到完game）<br />\n<br />\n遺言期間，除mc及死者外，任何人嚴禁插嘴...違者mc 處罰"},{"pid":"1abca0ee524e2917f2f748b153cd017835b37fd9","tid":467051,"uid":87480,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-13T14:06:43.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"98484499ed9eab380ae3ea2d95b60c07b72a523d","tid":467051,"uid":87480,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T01:15:17.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"ee828eae982b0b2b89366897b6ae094baab7c0a3","tid":467051,"uid":87480,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T01:24:07.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"7d16dc849865e1df9a917069a13018dfb18923af","tid":467051,"uid":87480,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T08:40:28.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"3c138d860bafc3dabfe5fa41268d4362a24d2e84","tid":467051,"uid":87480,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T01:21:41.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"02fb1ce06569c92d1abf22fab873bbeedf3c130b","tid":467051,"uid":87480,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T09:51:35.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"a2c24e9940772c8c145f6a1fb2e2ef8692f1ae62","tid":467051,"uid":87480,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T01:50:59.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"00de6548fef3c9daf102bec42b380d3036ad9563","tid":467051,"uid":87480,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-17T06:50:52.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"92002a64a24fea59d9d630fe8385f8a8b68dffeb","tid":467051,"uid":87480,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T03:57:32.000Z","msg":"."},{"pid":"53941a89af60b149e56f284238e493c6896fddc2","tid":467051,"uid":57797,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-18T04:01:18.000Z","msg":"on 撚 9咁撚麻煩 直接dl 個app 玩好撚過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fdfc599f2e2b3a96e3e13289c86fa9ec253af11","tid":467051,"uid":87480,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0